data.title: Nia Long: Movies, Photos, Videos, News, Biography & Birthday
data.meta_description: Nia Long: Check out the list of all Nia Long movies along with photos, videos, biography and birthday. Also find latest Nia Long news on Times of India.
data.text:
Will Smith says his new shirtless pic is "The Worst Shape of My Life"

ANI / May 03, 2021, 19:51 (IST)

Hollywood star Will Smith recently posted a shirtless picture of him on his social media account, claiming that it represents "the worst shape of my life."

Cara Delevingne sports bald look on 'Life in a Year' set

PTI / Apr 26, 2017, 15:43 (IST)

Model-turned-actress Cara Delevingne has shaved her head to get into her character for 'Life in a Year'

Cara Delevingne debuts pixie haircut

PTI / Apr 16, 2017, 16:44 (IST)

Model-turned-actress Cara Delevingne appeared in a new pastel pixie crop after hinting she would chop off her hair for new film role.

Will Smith chops off Jaden's dreadlocks

PTI / Apr 12, 2017, 16:01 (IST)

Hollywood star Will Smith has chopped off his son Jaden Smith's blonde hued dreadlocks for his upcoming film 'Life In A Year'

Demi Moore joins 'Empire' cast

PTI / Feb 22, 2017, 11:04 (IST)

Actress Demi Moore is set to make her debut in on the season three finale of the Fox hip-hop drama "Empire".

Jaafar Jackson dazzles as Uncle Michael in upcoming biopic: 'Michael'; wows cinemacon audience

Apr 11, 2024, 13:13 (IST)

The most striking aspect of the trailer is the performance of Jaafar Jackson, Michael Jackson's real-life nephew, who portrays his uncle with remarkable charisma and stage presence. Alongside Jaafar, the film features a talented ensemble cast, including Colman Domingo and Nia Long as Jackson's parents

Michael Jackson's nephew recreates 'Man in the Mirror' look in his biopic

ANI / Feb 14, 2024, 16:58 (IST)

Antoine Fuqua leads the talented team behind the Michael Jackson biopic 'Michael.' The film is produced by Graham King and the Michael Jackson estate's co-executives, with Lionsgate handling domestic release and Universal Pictures International distributing internationally. Jaafar Jackson paid a heartfelt tribute to his late uncle, Michael Jackson, by recreating the iconic 'Man in the Mirror' appearance from the 'Dangerous' tour of 1992-93 in a first look photo.

'You People' cast supports Jonah Hill's decision not to do press

ANI / Jan 19, 2023, 12:00 (IST)

Actor Jonah Hill's 'You People' co-stars have weighed in on his decision to not promote or do press for his films due to the toll it takes on his mental health.

Golden Globes recipient Eddie Murphy takes a dig at Will Smith over infamous Oscar slap

ANI / Jan 11, 2023, 16:09 (IST)

At the Golden Globes on Tuesday night, Eddie Murphy delivered a speech in which he accepted the Cecil B. DeMille Award and offered some helpful advice pieces for aspiring professionals in the industry.
